Text: JPMorgan Chase & Co. lifted its stake in shares of Travelzoo by 2,934.4% in the second quarter. JPMorgan Chase & Co. now owns 49,855 shares of the information services provider's stock valued at $764,000 after buying an additional 48,212 shares during the period.
